        "aboutme": {
          "markdown": {
            "html": "<p><strong>Hey!</strong></p>\n<p>I'm Diogo Torres Correia from Portugal!<br>\nI love programming, as well as running, taking photos and learning new things!<br>\nFeel free to get in touch or take a look at my past work below.</p>"
          }
        },
        "topProjects": {
          "nodes": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Triton is a Spigot plugin for Minecraft that enables a Minecraft server to send messages in the player's language.<br>\nThis was my first premium plugin on Spigot and I've put a lot of work and effort into it!</p>",
              "frontmatter": {
