            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Portugal Ultra Triathlon is a solidary adventure and a triple ironman. Its mission is to challenge participants' limits and their resilience, generate social value and supporting local communities.<br>\nI was behind the entire internet presence of the event, from the website itself down to the donation system and sysadmin work (setting up emails, custom domains, etc).</p>",
              "frontmatter": {
                "name": "Portugal Ultra Triathlon",
                "link": "https://portugalultratriathlon.com",
                "calltoaction": "Visit Website",
                "background": "#1b4d7b",
                "color": "#fff",
                "icon": {
                  "childImageSharp": {
                    "fixed": {
                      "base64": "data:image/png;base64,",
                      "width": 80,
                      "height": 80,
                      "src": "/static/b71a6dc009e44037c926d505aaeeafaa/8b091/put.png",
                      "srcSet": "/static/b71a6dc009e44037c926d505aaeeafaa/8b091/put.png 1x,\n/static/b71a6dc009e44037c926d505aaeeafaa/1e576/put.png 1.5x,\n/static/b71a6dc009e44037c926d505aaeeafaa/6cb10/put.png 2x",
                      "srcWebp": "/static/b71a6dc009e44037c926d505aaeeafaa/3a287/put.webp",
                      "srcSetWebp": "/static/b71a6dc009e44037c926d505aaeeafaa/3a287/put.webp 1x,\n/static/b71a6dc009e44037c926d505aaeeafaa/10741/put.webp 1.5x,\n/static/b71a6dc009e44037c926d505aaeeafaa/edc3c/put.webp 2x"
